consider this before buying.","The ICD-BX132 does have five file folders, so you can organize your files by subject. There is no mark tracking, but there is an easy search feature that allows you to rewind and fast-forward in short increments to more quickly find a quote or important segment of a lecture.","It also has a noise cut feature that limits background noise and digital pitch control, for faster playback without changing the pitch of a person&#39;s voice, which are both nice features. This is a mono recorder, so recording music won&#39;t be its strong point. However, there is an external microphone jack which will allow you to record in stereo if you want to purchase a separate microphone.","In addition to its online community, where many issues you may experience when using this device can be addressed, Sony provides support of all types including email, phone and chat."]},"id":"c096aa6b-e812-4b98-8c06-5c39798d841b","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"6debe9e9-208e-4d6c-85ae-27abde64245b","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This very affordable digital voice recorder has a remarkable internal storage capacity for a 2GB device. This partially makes up for what it lacks in terms of USB connectivity and SD card slot availability. A noise cut and easy search features are nice additions, but they don&#39;t quite make up for what is lacking."]},"id":"5436d4cf-f080-4b10-bb79-2777715b8838","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_57018","url":"/sony-icd-bx-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeph-preece","url":"/author/jeph-preece","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Jeph Preece","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"UEqrRM5xmXnCHCjkbS6o5e","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-07-16T13:47:56Z","datePublished":"2013-07-16T13:47:56Z","name":"Sony ICD-BX","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our lineup because it no long